attributes._cssText: .accordion { background-color: rgba(23, 151, 190, 0.2); margin-bottom: 3px; color: rgb(23, 151, 190); cursor: pointer; padding: 5px; width: 100%; text-align: left; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: middle; }.accordion:hover { background-color: rgba(23, 151, 190, 0.133); }.panel { overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.2s ease-out 0s; }.inputfile { width: 0.1px; height: 0.1px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; position: absolute; z-index: -1; }.inputfile + label { justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75em; display: inline-block; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; }.inputfile:focus + label, .inputfile + label:hover { background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); }.inputfile:focus + label { outline: -webkit-focus-ring-color auto 5px; }.inputfile + label { cursor: pointer; }.content-heading { justify-content: center; }.remove-row { background: none; border: none; margin-left: 0.35em; transition: color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 18px; }.remove-row:hover { color: rgb(23, 151, 190); cursor: pointer; }.row-wrapper { margin-top: 10px; }.new-instr { margin-right: 20px; }.new-instr, .new-data { padding-left: 0.35em; padding-right: 0.35em; width: 30%; }.add-step, .submit-button { margin-top: 10px; border-radius: 100px; color: rgb(23, 151, 190); background-color: white; border: 1px solid rgb(23, 151, 190); transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; font-weight: lighter; }.add-step:hover, .submit-button:hover { color: rgba(23, 151, 190, 0.533); border: 1px solid rgba(23, 151, 190, 0.533); cursor: pointer; }.new-textfield { border: 1px solid black; }.big-spinner { text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-top: 10%; color: rgb(23, 151, 190); }.loop { position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px; }.lightning { position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px; }#script-div { font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace; white-space: pre-line; }#response { font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; }
